headline: Ross Stores (ROST) Beats Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Ross Stores (ROST) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +12.86% and +3.47%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: As holidays approach, value players Walmart and T.J. Maxx are drawing the cash-strapped and the wealthy
summary: The retailers' performance jumps out as investors and economists try to predict the holiday season and the outlook for the U.S. economy next year.
